   767	        // effectively rank-deficient and the analytic VJP is undefined.
   768	        // Return zero gradients (the correct shrink-out limit) instead of
   769	        // raising — production training at large F can have individual
   770	        // atoms saturate λ in early batches and must not blow up here.
   771	        warn_ill_conditioned_backward_once(p, d, f64::INFINITY);
