   920	/// Numerically stable Euclidean norm of an `Array1<f64>`.
   921	///
   922	/// Used to assemble the penalized-gradient natural scale at every
   923	/// `WorkingState` construction site (main GAM, identity-link short circuit,
   924	/// survival, test mocks). Centralizing here avoids drift between sites and
   925	/// makes the convergence certificate's denominator a single source of truth.
