  1261	    /// coefficient. When set, the inner solver seeds `λ_LM` to this
  1262	    /// value instead of the default `1e-6`. Clamped on consumption to
  1263	    /// `[1e-6, 1e-3]` so a stale or pathological hint cannot poison the
  1264	    /// solve: the upper bound costs at most three damping halvings
  1265	    /// versus the cold default, which is dwarfed by the savings when
  1266	    /// the hint is informative.
  1267	    ///
