  1344	// Fixed stabilization ridge for PIRLS/PLS. `penalty_term` carries this as
  1345	// ridge * ||beta||^2 (equivalently 0.5 * ridge * ||beta||^2 in the
  1346	// 0.5 * (deviance + penalty_term) objective), and it is constant w.r.t. rho.
