  2494	/// XᵀWX = Σᵢ wᵢ · xᵢ xᵢᵀ. The matrix is symmetric, so only the upper triangle
  2495	/// needs to be computed; the only consumer (`assemble_upper`) filters to
  2496	/// row ≤ col. Two backends trade off in opposite memory regimes:
