  2498	/// * **Dense outer-product** (small p): allocate a dense p×p buffer and
  2499	///   accumulate one rank-1 update per data row. Per-row work is nnz(xᵢ)² —
  2500	///   for B-spline-style designs this dominates SpGEMM by orders of magnitude.
