   265	/// Abstract interface for Hessian linear algebra operations.
   266	///
   267	/// All operations use the SAME internal decomposition, ensuring spectral
   268	/// consistency between logdet (used in cost) and trace/solve (used in gradient).
   269	///
   270	/// Implementors:
