   697	    /// Batched cross traces for the logdet Hessian:
   698	    /// `cross[i,j] = trace_logdet_hessian_cross(H_i, H_j)`.
   699	    ///
   700	    /// The default implementation applies `trace_logdet_hessian_cross`
   701	    /// pairwise. Dense spectral backends override this to rotate each drift
   702	    /// into the eigenbasis once and reuse the same divided-difference kernel
   703	    /// across all pairs.
